data.description: Amazing 36+ acre property with 2 Homes and additional living space above oversized garage. Multi-family or income property conveniently located just 3 miles from Hwy 12. Pristine mountain views of the Spanish Peaks as well as the meadow and a seasonal creek below. This unique property has 2 wonderful homes built along the ridge to enjoy amazing views. The main home is warm and inviting as well as open and airy. Enjoy the beautiful sunrise and sunsets from either covered porch. The expansive great room with floor to ceiling windows provides ample natural light. There is a bedroom and bathroom on each level with many multi-use spaces  throughout. The oversized garage allows space for a workshop as well as an apartment above, including a bathroom. The log cabin guest house offers 3 levels with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. As an income property, or a personal family retreat, the potential for this property is endless.
